E-01 UPDATE INST IS WRONG.<0= CANCEL   1= CHANGE. 2= ADD>
E-02 MATERIAL CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-03 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS DELETED M/F ALREADY
E-04 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOES NOT EXIST
E-05 A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT IT IS DELETED M/F ALREADY
E-06 A CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOES NOT EXIST
E-07 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F IS REGISTERED ALREADY
E-08 MATERIAL PURCHASE UNIT PRICE IS NOT INPUT
E-09 CLIPPING SALE UNP INPUT, BUT COLLECTION RATE IS NOT
E-10 CLIPPING COLLECTION RATE INPUT, BUT SALE UNP IS NOT
E-11 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED CUSTOMER EXCEPT ADDITION
E-12 UPD INST- CAN NOT INPUT COPIED FACTORY EXCEPT ADDTION.
